{"tid":1769180,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"( 黃店馬拉松）挑戰全日都剩係幫襯黃店 Day 1","createTime":"2019-12-04T16:08:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-05T01:00:35.000Z","uid":45206,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"028cf0d8980f175843a9158bcc49cffb5f1df5d6","tid":1769180,"uid":45206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T16:08:23.000Z","msg":"見到黃色經濟圈逐漸形成，好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我決定每日都淨係喺黃店消費，身體力行睇下有乜嘢可以再進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n9:00 起身返工，坐九巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nLunch time 冇咩胃口，唔食，去黃店一芳買咗杯嘢飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n諗起隻貓冇貓砂，然後打開黃店app<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gKVYmn0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgKVYmn0.png&h=7eb72de1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n搵到一間附近嘅黃店賣貓用品<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1b6QcuT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1b6QcuT.png&h=63f923c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於我個人小心謹慎，所以自己google fact check<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/43Q9s3o.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F43Q9s3o.png&h=d71ae5e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n確保無誤之後，上門買咗貓砂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/owXf73M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FowXf73M.jpg&h=e56d3738&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NV4us3U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNV4us3U.jpg&h=f9ad32e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n返工返到個頭油油哋，之後到首領誠哥開嘅家居用品店watsons，買咗一支dry shampoo<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QfRQcv7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQfRQcv7.jpg&h=1ebd028f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢啲嘢喺我樓下藥房賣20蚊，誠哥賣40蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係冇咩所謂，如果你唔係黃店，我射落海都唔會益你。 你係黃店，貴一倍我都心甘情願<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後收工返屋企搭九巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30510936b8d9fcd42bde536855f0543de973d6a6","tid":1769180,"uid":45206,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T16:11:12.000Z","msg":"然後屋企人話要搵間好少少嘅中菜廳食飯<br />\n<br />\n問題就嚟喇<br />\n<br />\n我發現原來冇乜嘢中價嘅中菜廳係黃店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n於是我哋求其搵咗一間冇表態嘅中菜廳食飯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"445e37562732d1deeb409ab314531d2b6eb40564","tid":1769180,"uid":73212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T16:11:56.000Z","msg":"對唔住，借個位宣傳一下。<br />\n<br />\n[ 國際戰缐 ] 歐洲巡迴展覧團隊眾籌！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1768712/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1768712/page/1</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a16769c1bde3c5602b05a279f1a2a8e80cc6994d","tid":1769180,"uid":45206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"445e37562732d1deeb409ab314531d2b6eb40564","tid":1769180,"uid":73212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T16:11:56.000Z","msg":"對唔住，借個位宣傳一下。<br />\n<br />\n[ 國際戰缐 ] 歐洲巡迴展覧團隊眾籌！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1768712/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1768712/page/1</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-1